title: DJ James Kennedy
description:
James Kennedy returns, and he and Lala take a trip down memory lane, reliving some of their wild moments from their early days on #PumpRules, shedding some light on their instant chemistry and why their relationship only went so far, and explaining the profound moment in Big Bear that Lala wishes she would have taken seriously back then. James also shares his thoughts on the recent season of #PumpRules, his break-up with Raquel Leviss, and the current state of his dating life. Plus, Lala answers your voicemails about mocktails, confidence, and killing it in job interviews!
